comment: Lemma for ~ 4001prm . Calculate a power mod. In decimal, we calculate ` 2 ^ 1 0 0 0 = 2 ^ 8 0 0 x. 2 ^ 2 0 0 == 2 3 1 1 x. 9 0 2 ` ` = 5 2 1 N + 1 ` and finally ` 2 ^ ( N - 1 ) = ( 2 ^ 1 0 0 0 ) ^ 4 == 1 ^ 4 = 1 ` . (Contributed by Mario Carneiro, 3-Mar-2014.) (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 20-Apr-2015.) (Proof shortened by AV, 16-Sep-2021.)
